1
00:00:19,092 --> 00:00:19,732
Wei,

2
00:00:19,732 --> 00:00:21,133
Su Yunian has left home.

3
00:00:21,133 --> 00:00:22,052
Shall we take action?

4
00:00:23,372 --> 00:00:24,052
Go ahead.

5
00:00:24,212 --> 00:00:24,812
Yes.

6
00:00:34,492 --> 00:00:35,852
Wei, I checked again.

7
00:00:35,852 --> 00:00:36,652
Nothing found.

8
00:00:50,092 --> 00:00:50,813
Feng,

9
00:00:51,253 --> 00:00:53,293
we've searched and found nothing.

10
00:00:54,452 --> 00:00:55,132
Mr. Tu,

11
00:00:56,173 --> 00:00:56,973
are you there?

12
00:00:58,692 --> 00:00:59,412
Mr. Tu?

13
00:01:07,253 --> 00:01:07,853
Mr. Tu,

14
00:01:07,893 --> 00:01:08,613
are you there?

15
00:01:09,813 --> 00:01:10,613
I'm coming in.

16
00:01:17,173 --> 00:01:17,813
Mr. Tu?

17
00:01:48,013 --> 00:01:49,013
(Seems)

18
00:01:49,412 --> 00:01:50,973
(this is the backup wristband.)

19
00:02:17,933 --> 00:02:20,608
(So she still doesn't trust me.)

20
00:02:33,612 --> 00:02:34,533
So,

21
00:02:34,852 --> 00:02:37,452
the wristband Mr. Tu claims
he never liked wearing

22
00:02:38,612 --> 00:02:39,692
is actually the backup one.

23
00:02:41,452 --> 00:02:42,852
You've never actually seen

24
00:02:42,852 --> 00:02:44,012
his exclusive wristband,

25
00:02:44,093 --> 00:02:45,132
namely the one

26
00:02:45,132 --> 00:02:47,253
in the police evidence bag days ago?

27
00:02:47,892 --> 00:02:48,973
That seems to be the case.

28
00:02:49,813 --> 00:02:52,093
But this doesn't completely confirm

29
00:02:52,093 --> 00:02:53,692
Tu Jiasheng went to the crime scene.

30
00:02:54,292 --> 00:02:55,533
What if someone stole his

31
00:02:55,533 --> 00:02:56,653
to intentionally frame him?

32
00:02:56,773 --> 00:02:57,732
It may well be possible.

33
00:03:00,933 --> 00:03:01,572
Makes sense.

34
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:05,984
=The Glory Fades=

35
00:03:05,984 --> 00:03:08,000
=Episode 30=
(Going to the Appointment)

36
00:03:08,333 --> 00:03:09,292
But that doesn't add up.

37
00:03:10,093 --> 00:03:11,892
Then why did he choose Ruoxi back then?

38
00:03:13,053 --> 00:03:15,012
It doesn't fit
his ladder-climbing principle.

39
00:03:18,572 --> 00:03:20,452
That's the crux of the problem.

40
00:03:22,172 --> 00:03:23,012
It's said

41
00:03:23,012 --> 00:03:25,572
the Grand Princess strongly opposed
Paria marrying beneath her,

42
00:03:26,572 --> 00:03:28,653
but Paria was infatuated
with Tu Jiasheng.

43
00:03:29,172 --> 00:03:29,973
Later,

44
00:03:30,653 --> 00:03:31,892
as Ruoxi appeared,

45
00:03:32,253 --> 00:03:33,292
Paria finally let go.

46
00:03:35,333 --> 00:03:38,813
Seems Ruoxi's charm...

47
00:03:39,253 --> 00:03:40,333
Downright horrifying.

48
00:03:42,373 --> 00:03:43,253
Doesn't make sense.

49
00:03:43,933 --> 00:03:44,692
Could it be

50
00:03:45,213 --> 00:03:45,973
that he

51
00:03:45,973 --> 00:03:47,852
just used Ruoxi as a tool,

52
00:03:47,852 --> 00:03:49,333
to refuse the Grand Princess?

53
00:03:49,333 --> 00:03:50,452
And in reality...

54
00:04:02,933 --> 00:04:04,933
We haven't had a drink alone in ages.

55
00:04:09,373 --> 00:04:09,933
Lu,

56
00:04:10,852 --> 00:04:11,933
I want to talk with you.

57
00:04:14,572 --> 00:04:16,253
Feng can't stay hidden forever.

58
00:04:17,533 --> 00:04:18,373
He sought you out.

59
00:04:19,132 --> 00:04:20,533
He'll definitely come for me next.

60
00:04:22,252 --> 00:04:23,893
If anything unexpected happens,

61
00:04:24,453 --> 00:04:26,573
Deep In The Bustle must keep operating.

62
00:04:28,372 --> 00:04:30,133
It can't stop because of me.

63
00:04:33,852 --> 00:04:35,453
Why are you somber today?

64
00:04:36,773 --> 00:04:38,133
Has something happened?

65
00:04:43,172 --> 00:04:44,013
Su Yunian

66
00:04:44,492 --> 00:04:45,893
is An Ruoxi's biological sister.

67
00:04:46,133 --> 00:04:46,812
Did you know?

68
00:04:48,372 --> 00:04:49,653
The identical look says it all.

69
00:04:51,052 --> 00:04:52,333
You didn't drive her away,

70
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:53,492
so we kept silent.

71
00:04:53,893 --> 00:04:55,893
Then you must also know why she came.

72
00:04:56,372 --> 00:04:57,573
To investigate Ruoxi's case.

73
00:04:58,573 --> 00:04:59,812
You two are so close now.

74
00:05:00,893 --> 00:05:02,052
What's your reservations?

75
00:05:03,292 --> 00:05:04,693
I don't fear her investigation,

76
00:05:05,492 --> 00:05:06,372
but I fear

77
00:05:08,573 --> 00:05:09,653
she's being used by others.

78
00:05:11,893 --> 00:05:12,773
You mean Feng?

79
00:05:20,573 --> 00:05:21,893
I'm telling you this

80
00:05:21,893 --> 00:05:23,453
to help you sort things out.

81
00:05:24,133 --> 00:05:26,133
We can't confirm directly right now

82
00:05:26,133 --> 00:05:28,133
that Tu Jiasheng is the murderer, right?

83
00:05:29,133 --> 00:05:30,653
Moreover, you just said

84
00:05:30,812 --> 00:05:32,732
Chu Bai met with Chief Zheng.

85
00:05:33,573 --> 00:05:35,052
Chief Zheng arranged everything.

86
00:05:35,893 --> 00:05:37,412
Why would Chief Zheng help you?

87
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:39,573
What's in it for him?

88
00:05:41,773 --> 00:05:43,093
None at all.

89
00:05:43,093 --> 00:05:44,492
Only a lot of downsides, right?

90
00:05:45,453 --> 00:05:46,653
Back then, he came

91
00:05:47,133 --> 00:05:49,013
to the conclusion mentally ill person

92
00:05:49,172 --> 00:05:50,292
was the murderer.

93
00:05:50,852 --> 00:05:52,133
Now he supports you

94
00:05:52,812 --> 00:05:53,932
in uncovering the truth,

95
00:05:53,932 --> 00:05:54,932
and provides evidence?

96
00:05:54,932 --> 00:05:55,492
Do you think

97
00:05:55,893 --> 00:05:56,612
that's reasonable?

98
00:05:57,773 --> 00:05:58,732
Conscience awakening

99
00:05:58,732 --> 00:05:59,852
or just brain-dead?

100
00:06:01,453 --> 00:06:02,932
Only one explanation makes sense.

101
00:06:04,013 --> 00:06:04,612
What?

102
00:06:05,492 --> 00:06:06,213
Chief Zheng

103
00:06:06,732 --> 00:06:08,252
was set up to do this.

104
00:06:08,533 --> 00:06:09,773
He was being controlled.

105
00:06:11,453 --> 00:06:13,573
Those who blocked the investigation
back then

106
00:06:14,133 --> 00:06:15,932
are requesting the investigation now.

107
00:06:16,773 --> 00:06:17,932
The investigation

108
00:06:18,052 --> 00:06:18,812
was

109
00:06:19,213 --> 00:06:21,533
never to uncover the truth
about Ruoxi's death.

110
00:06:25,344 --> 00:06:27,488
(Chu Bai calling)

111
00:06:28,573 --> 00:06:29,093
Hello.

112
00:06:29,573 --> 00:06:30,852
The fingerprint film is ready.

113
00:06:31,133 --> 00:06:32,812
I need to hack into Room 999's computer

114
00:06:32,812 --> 00:06:33,812
to find the evidence.

115
00:06:35,172 --> 00:06:36,213
What do you need me to do?

116
00:06:36,773 --> 00:06:38,372
I need you to play along in an act.

117
00:06:38,612 --> 00:06:39,773
Let's meet and talk.

118
00:06:40,612 --> 00:06:41,093
Okay.

119
00:06:41,573 --> 00:06:42,412
Usual spot.

120
00:06:44,372 --> 00:06:45,052
Chu Bai?

121
00:07:47,812 --> 00:07:48,492
Lu,

122
00:07:52,812 --> 00:07:54,172
I need to tell you something.

123
00:07:57,172 --> 00:07:58,612
Hiding a few secrets over the years.

124
00:07:59,372 --> 00:07:59,852
Go ahead.

125
00:08:03,172 --> 00:08:04,372
The Grand Princess...

126
00:08:20,292 --> 00:08:20,773
Hello,

127
00:08:21,093 --> 00:08:21,732
who is this?

128
00:08:21,732 --> 00:08:23,693
Who does it show on your end,

129
00:08:23,812 --> 00:08:24,893
Jiasheng?

130
00:08:32,372 --> 00:08:33,172
You're not dead?

131
00:08:33,372 --> 00:08:34,172
Want me dead?

132
00:08:35,052 --> 00:08:37,052
That wasn't so easy to arrange.

133
00:08:39,892 --> 00:08:41,012
I thought you did it?

134
00:08:41,772 --> 00:08:43,372
The death report was filed. Zheng...

135
00:08:46,093 --> 00:08:47,456
Finally putting it together, huh?

136
00:08:47,892 --> 00:08:49,333
Jiasheng, Lu,

137
00:08:49,732 --> 00:08:51,413
I must say, your memories

138
00:08:51,573 --> 00:08:53,813
are truly terrible.

139
00:08:53,892 --> 00:08:55,573
Chief Zheng's mentor

140
00:08:56,413 --> 00:08:59,232
was Feng's father.

141
00:09:08,333 --> 00:09:09,173
What do you want?

142
00:09:09,372 --> 00:09:10,772
Feng said

143
00:09:11,813 --> 00:09:12,973
it's time to meet,

144
00:09:13,852 --> 00:09:15,213
and settle this once and for all.

145
00:09:16,132 --> 00:09:16,933
When?

146
00:09:17,213 --> 00:09:18,732
Right here, right now.

147
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:20,333
This very moment.

148
00:09:25,612 --> 00:09:27,093
Come to Deep In The Bustle with Feng.

149
00:09:27,573 --> 00:09:28,892
Come to his clubhouse.

150
00:09:29,053 --> 00:09:30,293
Mr. Zhao knows the address.

151
00:09:32,693 --> 00:09:34,012
Let me repeat.

152
00:09:34,813 --> 00:09:36,852
Come to Deep In The Bustle with Feng.

153
00:09:37,372 --> 00:09:38,413
This is his home.

154
00:09:38,573 --> 00:09:39,372
Anything to say,

155
00:09:39,372 --> 00:09:40,333
say it at home.

156
00:09:40,333 --> 00:09:41,333
Mr. Tu,

157
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,012
help me!

158
00:09:43,813 --> 00:09:44,813
Jiasheng,

159
00:09:44,973 --> 00:09:46,053
no more nonsense.

160
00:09:46,372 --> 00:09:47,573
You have

161
00:09:48,173 --> 00:09:52,333
one hour.

162
00:09:58,933 --> 00:09:59,532
Jiasheng,

163
00:10:00,772 --> 00:10:01,772
I need to talk to you.

164
00:10:02,813 --> 00:10:03,293
Lu,

165
00:10:04,532 --> 00:10:05,532
tell me after I get back.

166
00:10:10,453 --> 00:10:11,093
Jiasheng,

167
00:10:12,173 --> 00:10:13,372
let me go with you!

168
00:10:14,732 --> 00:10:15,573
We can't both go.

169
00:10:16,173 --> 00:10:17,173
Someone has to stay here.

170
00:10:19,612 --> 00:10:22,012
Deep In The Bustle is in your hands now.

171
00:10:42,413 --> 00:10:44,544
I owe you my life.

172
00:11:41,472 --> 00:11:42,053
Hello.

173
00:11:42,573 --> 00:11:43,293
What's wrong, Dad?

174
00:11:43,532 --> 00:11:44,293
Where are you?

175
00:11:44,933 --> 00:11:46,144
Are you with Tu Jiasheng?

176
00:11:46,293 --> 00:11:47,492
No, I'm in the car.

177
00:11:49,012 --> 00:11:50,293
Don't contact me for a while.

178
00:11:50,933 --> 00:11:52,053
Don't cause any trouble,

179
00:11:52,544 --> 00:11:53,933
and don't go home. Understand?

180
00:11:55,933 --> 00:11:56,732
Did you hear me?

181
00:11:57,216 --> 00:11:58,173
What happened?

182
00:11:58,973 --> 00:11:59,933
Listen,

183
00:12:00,512 --> 00:12:01,772
the inspection team is here.

184
00:12:03,413 --> 00:12:04,213
From the Cabinet?

185
00:12:04,892 --> 00:12:06,252
Didn't you get any prior notice?

186
00:12:06,852 --> 00:12:07,772
That puzzles me too.

187
00:12:08,064 --> 00:12:08,732
Normally,

188
00:12:08,732 --> 00:12:10,612
the Grand Princess
handles these matters.

189
00:12:11,173 --> 00:12:12,173
With Tu Jiasheng around,

190
00:12:12,173 --> 00:12:13,933
she should've given us
a heads-up at least.

191
00:12:14,532 --> 00:12:16,772
Maybe he hasn't been in touch
with her lately?

192
00:12:17,012 --> 00:12:17,973
I'll go tell him.

193
00:12:18,772 --> 00:12:20,852
Do you know
who's leading the inspection team?

194
00:12:21,612 --> 00:12:22,132
Who?

195
00:12:23,173 --> 00:12:24,173
Nie Feng's father.

196
00:12:25,252 --> 00:12:25,732
So,

197
00:12:25,732 --> 00:12:27,252
call Feng.

198
00:12:28,064 --> 00:12:28,612
By the way,

199
00:12:29,213 --> 00:12:30,973
any word on his return recently?

200
00:12:31,813 --> 00:12:32,892
I'm asking you.

201
00:12:35,573 --> 00:12:36,492
Okay, I got it, Dad.

202
00:12:37,173 --> 00:12:37,772
I'll tell him.

203
00:12:37,772 --> 00:12:38,492
Take care.

204
00:12:43,213 --> 00:12:44,293
Seems Feng

205
00:12:45,012 --> 00:12:46,813
let your dad make you choose sides.

206
00:13:20,608 --> 00:13:21,333
Chu Bai,

207
00:13:22,012 --> 00:13:22,612
go upstairs.

208
00:13:38,068 --> 00:13:41,742
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

209
00:13:42,041 --> 00:13:45,232
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

210
00:13:47,064 --> 00:13:50,685
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

211
00:13:51,234 --> 00:13:54,033
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

212
00:13:55,504 --> 00:13:59,234
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

213
00:13:59,458 --> 00:14:02,955
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

214
00:14:04,354 --> 00:14:08,041
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

215
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:13,794
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

216
00:14:14,498 --> 00:14:18,632
♪I feel guilty♪

217
00:14:19,202 --> 00:14:22,946
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

218
00:14:23,810 --> 00:14:27,253
♪Even in tears♪

219
00:14:28,002 --> 00:14:31,916
♪It doesn't matter♪

220
00:14:32,098 --> 00:14:35,921
♪We embrace in dreams♪

221
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:40,208
♪I let down all my defenses♪

222
00:14:41,442 --> 00:14:44,805
♪Though the story has its end♪

223
00:14:45,570 --> 00:14:53,922
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
